snippet.textDisplay:
ગોતિલો
Gotvanu= to find 
Lo= honorific way to command someone 
Conjugation—> gotilo गोतिलो means you’re commanding someone politely to find something or someone. 

You guys are seriously immature if you think that’s remotely funny. It’s not even pronounced the same but regardless, other languages do not cater to your own.
